org.trianacode.enactment

Class TrianaRun

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.trianacode.enactment.TrianaRun

  • public class TrianaRun
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for running a taskgraph. Unlike TrianaExec, TrianaRun does not handle synchronuizing between multiple invocations.
